           - Made QtWvDialer compile with Qt-3.x
           - some chrome

19/07/2004 Version 0.4.1
           - Improved logfile viewer

26/07/2004 Version 0.4.2
           - Mainwindow usability
           - Removed copyright window
             (is page in config dialog now)
           - made graph reflect connection state

16/10/2004 Version 0.4.3
           - Typo in email address (AUTHORS file)
           - Reflect usage of Qt3.x in INSTALL

04/02/2007 Version 0.4.4
